{"tid":422378,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[佔中真相］旺角佔領區就是破壞了30年來民主運動的心血！","createTime":"2017-10-03T04:12:23.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-03T04:20:18.000Z","uid":49388,"like":0,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"bb607fe18b5b571ed97bc2162bad25d0d3222467","tid":422378,"uid":49388,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T04:12:23.000Z","msg":"佔中是香港有史以來最大型的民主運動<br />\n<br />\n一大批良心正義市民響應戴耀延教授出來佔中，但可借既係情況失控，有人衝動地佔理旺角，令整埸佔中一發不可收拾，並不停有打鬥場面，嚇壞小孩，有失分數！<br />\n<br />\n有見及此，佔中三子及其民主英雄為保運動決定收復失地，拎只旺角佔領區主導權，並多次呼籲立即撒離旺角返回金鐘以展示團結再解散保元氣，可惜多次都被有心人阻止！<br />\n<br />\n結果佔中膠著，最後盡失民意，失敗收場<br />\n<br />\n所以旺角佔領區就是破壞了30年來民主運動的心血！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8de27b383b81aac7af504e6a57d66681ae56f7e5","tid":422378,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T04:20:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/03/122005_c3e6b8f11dbbf0b0be33b197495668f7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F03%2F122005_c3e6b8f11dbbf0b0be33b197495668f7.jpg&h=57394ff4&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/03/122016_2cb54acc54a46f1bd0184c0b406ca3c0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F03%2F122016_2cb54acc54a46f1bd0184c0b406ca3c0.jpg&h=f8764422&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}